Class ExpConstraint

Direct Known Subclasses:
EqExpConstraint, GeExpConstraint, GtExpConstraint, LeExpConstraint, LtExpConstraint, NeExpConstraint
public abstract class ExpConstraint
extends Constraint

Abstract Expression class. It is meant to be extended to create new expression types.
Expressions have exactly 2 Eval operands.
